{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":499,"text":"In the spring of 2016,"},{"time":3046,"text":"a legal battle between Apple\nand the Federal Bureau of Investigation"},{"time":7474,"text":"captured the world's attention."}]},{"cues":[{"time":9633,"text":"Apple has built security features\ninto its mobile products"},{"time":12996,"text":"which protect data on its devices\nfrom everyone but the owner."},{"time":16853,"text":"That means that criminals, hackers\nand yes, even governments"},{"time":21522,"text":"are all locked out."},{"time":23580,"text":"For Apple's customers,\nthis is a great thing."},{"time":26581,"text":"But governments are not so happy."},{"time":29152,"text":"You see, Apple has made\na conscious decision"},{"time":31493,"text":"to get out of the surveillance business."},{"time":34077,"text":"Apple has tried to make surveillance\nas difficult as possible"},{"time":37312,"text":"for governments and any other actors."}]},{"cues":[{"time":41676,"text":"There are really two\nsmartphone operating systems"},{"time":44030,"text":"in the global smartphone market:"},{"time":45682,"text":"iOS and Android."},{"time":47749,"text":"iOS is made by Apple.\nAndroid is made by Google."},{"time":51446,"text":"Apple has spent a lot of time and money"},{"time":54594,"text":"to make sure that its products\nare as secure as possible."},{"time":58458,"text":"Apple encrypts all data\nstored on iPhones by default,"},{"time":61916,"text":"and text messages sent from one\nApple customer to another Apple customer"},{"time":65946,"text":"are encrypted by default"},{"time":67672,"text":"without the user having\nto take any actions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":70769,"text":"What this means is that,"},{"time":72404,"text":"if the police seize an iPhone\nand it has a password,"},{"time":76724,"text":"they'll have a difficult time\ngetting any data off of it,"},{"time":80390,"text":"if they can do it at all."},{"time":82374,"text":"In contrast, the security of Android\njust really isn't as good."},{"time":86536,"text":"Android phones, or at least\nmost of the Android phones"},{"time":89606,"text":"that have been sold to consumers,"},{"time":91236,"text":"do not encrypt data stored\non the device by default,"},{"time":94115,"text":"and the built-in text messaging app\nin Android does not use encryption."},{"time":99555,"text":"So if the police seize an Android phone,"},{"time":102273,"text":"chances are, they'll be able to get\nall the data they want"},{"time":105654,"text":"off of that device."}]},{"cues":[{"time":107858,"text":"Two smartphones"},{"time":109568,"text":"from two of the biggest\ncompanies in the world;"},{"time":112497,"text":"one that protects data by default,"},{"time":114948,"text":"and one that doesn't."}]},{"cues":[{"time":116840,"text":"Apple is a seller of luxury goods."},{"time":120006,"text":"It dominates the high end of the market."},{"time":122710,"text":"And we would expect a manufacturer\nof luxury goods to have products"},{"time":127088,"text":"that include more features."},{"time":129567,"text":"But not everyone can afford an iPhone."},{"time":131998,"text":"That's where Android\nreally, really dominates:"},{"time":134609,"text":"at the middle and low end of the market,"},{"time":137384,"text":"smartphones for the billion\nand a half people"},{"time":140034,"text":"who cannot or will not spend"},{"time":142928,"text":"600 dollars on a phone."}]},{"cues":[{"time":149275,"text":"But the dominance of Android\nhas led to what I call"},{"time":155129,"text":"the \"digital security divide.\""},{"time":157365,"text":"That is, there is now increasingly a gap"},{"time":160374,"text":"between the privacy\nand security of the rich,"},{"time":164523,"text":"who can afford devices\nthat secure their data by default,"},{"time":168036,"text":"and of the poor,"},{"time":169851,"text":"whose devices do very little\nto protect them by default."}]},{"cues":[{"time":175667,"text":"So, think of the average Apple customer:"},{"time":180013,"text":"a banker, a lawyer,\na doctor, a politician."},{"time":185387,"text":"These individuals now increasingly have\nsmartphones in their pockets"},{"time":190665,"text":"that encrypt their calls,\ntheir text messages,"},{"time":194162,"text":"all the data on the device,"},{"time":195721,"text":"without them doing really anything\nto secure their information."},{"time":200904,"text":"In contrast, the poor\nand the most vulnerable in our societies"},{"time":204973,"text":"are using devices that leave them\ncompletely vulnerable to surveillance."}]},{"cues":[{"time":211065,"text":"In the United States, where I live,"},{"time":213078,"text":"African-Americans are more likely\nto be seen as suspicious"},{"time":217051,"text":"or more likely to be profiled,"},{"time":219640,"text":"and are more likely to be targeted\nby the state with surveillance."},{"time":224008,"text":"But African-Americans\nare also disproportionately likely"},{"time":226821,"text":"to use Android devices\nthat do nothing at all"},{"time":229941,"text":"to protect them from that surveillance."},{"time":232974,"text":"This is a problem."}]},{"cues":[{"time":235536,"text":"We must remember\nthat surveillance is a tool."},{"time":238810,"text":"It's a tool used by those in power"},{"time":241934,"text":"against those who have no power."},{"time":245173,"text":"And while I think it's absolutely great"},{"time":249947,"text":"that companies like Apple\nare making it easy for people to encrypt,"},{"time":254355,"text":"if the only people\nwho can protect themselves"},{"time":258194,"text":"from the gaze of the government"},{"time":259709,"text":"are the rich and powerful,"},{"time":261741,"text":"that's a problem."},{"time":263549,"text":"And it's not just a privacy\nor a cybersecurity problem."},{"time":267739,"text":"It's a civil rights problem."}]},{"cues":[{"time":270806,"text":"So the lack of default security in Android"},{"time":273697,"text":"is not just a problem\nfor the poor and vulnerable users"},{"time":279100,"text":"who are depending on these devices."},{"time":281342,"text":"This is actually a problem\nfor our democracy."},{"time":284237,"text":"I'll explain what I mean."}]},{"cues":[{"time":286514,"text":"Modern social movements\nrely on technology --"},{"time":289413,"text":"from Black Lives Matter to the Arab Spring\nto Occupy Wall Street."},{"time":295238,"text":"The organizers of these movements\nand the members of these movements"},{"time":299237,"text":"increasingly communicate\nand coordinate with smartphones."},{"time":304446,"text":"And so, naturally governments\nthat feel threatened by these movements"},{"time":308321,"text":"will also target the organizers\nand their smartphones."},{"time":313462,"text":"Now, it's quite possible"},{"time":315560,"text":"that a future Martin Luther King\nor a Mandela or a Gandhi"},{"time":319648,"text":"will have an iPhone and be protected\nfrom government surveillance."},{"time":324283,"text":"But chances are,"},{"time":325854,"text":"they'll probably have a cheap,\n$20 Android phone in their pocket."}]},{"cues":[{"time":330676,"text":"And so if we do nothing\nto address the digital security divide,"},{"time":334521,"text":"if we do nothing to ensure\nthat everyone in our society"},{"time":339167,"text":"gets the same benefits of encryption"},{"time":341476,"text":"and is equally able to protect themselves\nfrom surveillance by the state,"},{"time":345157,"text":"not only will the poor and vulnerable\nbe exposed to surveillance,"},{"time":350404,"text":"but future civil rights\nmovements may be crushed"},{"time":353369,"text":"before they ever reach\ntheir full potential."}]},{"cues":[{"time":355813,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":357004,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":363940,"text":"Helen Walters: Chris, thank you so much."},{"time":365890,"text":"I have a question for you."},{"time":367786,"text":"We saw recently in the press"},{"time":369663,"text":"that Mark Zuckerberg from Facebook\ncovers over his camera"},{"time":375191,"text":"and does something\nwith his headphone mic jack."},{"time":378189,"text":"So I wanted to ask you\na personal question, which is:"},{"time":380758,"text":"Do you do that?"},{"time":381934,"text":"And, on behalf of everyone\nhere, particularly myself,"},{"time":384537,"text":"Should we be doing that?"},{"time":385886,"text":"Should we be covering these things?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":387678,"text":"Christopher Soghoian: Putting a sticker --\nactually, I like Band-Aids,"},{"time":391863,"text":"because you can remove them\nand put them back on"},{"time":394152,"text":"whenever you want to make\na call or a Skype call."},{"time":396488,"text":"Putting a sticker over your web cam"},{"time":398214,"text":"is probably the best thing\nyou can do for your privacy"},{"time":400914,"text":"in terms of bang for buck."},{"time":402444,"text":"There really is malware,\nmalicious software out there"},{"time":406365,"text":"that can take over your web cam,"},{"time":408246,"text":"even without the light turning on."},{"time":410140,"text":"This is used by criminals.\nThis is used by stalkers."},{"time":413333,"text":"You can buy $19.99 \"spy\non your ex-girlfriend\" software online."},{"time":418295,"text":"It's really terrifying."},{"time":419470,"text":"And then, of course,\nit's used by governments."},{"time":422018,"text":"And there's obviously\na sexual violence component to this,"},{"time":425263,"text":"which is that this kind of surveillance\ncan be used most effectively"},{"time":428988,"text":"against women and other people\nwho can be shamed in our society."},{"time":436417,"text":"Even if you think\nyou have nothing to hide,"},{"time":438549,"text":"at the very least, if you have\nchildren, teenagers in your lives,"},{"time":443131,"text":"make sure you put a sticker\non their camera and protect them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":446165,"text":"HW: Wow. Thank you so much.\nCS: Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":448183,"text":"HW: Thanks, Chris."}]},{"cues":[{"time":449358,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}